[256.240808, "o", "<p><!--\r\nQBlastInfoBegin\r\n\tStatus=READY\r\nQBlastInfoEnd\r\n--><p>\r\n<PRE>\r\n\r\nBLASTP 2.17.0+\r\nReference: Stephen F. Altschul, Thomas L. Madden, Alejandro\r\nA. Schaffer, Jinghui Zhang, Zheng Zhang, Webb Miller, and\r\nDavid J. Lipman (1997), \"Gapped BLAST and PSI-BLAST: a new\r\ngeneration of protein database search programs\", Nucleic\r\nAcids Res. 25:3389-3402.\r\n\r\n\r\nReference for compositional score matrix adjustment: Stephen\r\nF. Altschul, John C. Wootton, E. Michael Gertz, Richa\r\nAgarwala, Aleksandr Morgulis, Alejandro A. Schaffer, and\r\nYi-Kuo Yu (2005) \"Protein database searches using\r\ncompositionally adjusted substitution matrices\", FEBS J.\r\n272:5101-5109.\r\n\r\n\r\nRID: 4W05HNJN014\r\n\r\n\r\nDatabase: All non-redundant GenBank CDS\r\ntranslations+PDB+SwissProt+PIR+PRF excluding environmental samples\r\nfrom WGS projects\r\n           1,120,323,714 sequences; 422,831,240,217 total letters\r\nQuery= \r\nLength=228\r\n\r\n\r\n                                                                   Score     E      Max\r\nSequences producing significant alignments:                       (Bits)  Value   Ident\r\n\r\n8RMO_H Chain H, anti-FLAG M2 heavy chain [Mus musculus]            466     2e-165  100%      \r\n7BG1_H Chain H, anti-FLAG M2 heavy chain [Mus musculus]            441     1e-155  100%      \r\n1E6J_H Chain H, IMMUNOGLOBULIN [Mus musculus]                      377     4e-130  89%       \r\n8DCN_A Chain A, BINTOXB/9 Fab heavy chain [Mus musculus]           376     1e-129  89%       \r\n7W71_H Chain H, Heavy chain of Fab [Mus musculus]                  374     6e-129  89%       \r\nABR32159.1 anti-cucumber mosaic virus immunoglobulin heavy cha...  367     2e-126  88%       \r\n2I9L_B Chain B, Antibody 7D11 heavy chain [Mus musculus]           367     2e-126  87%       \r\n5VGA_B Chain B, Fab 36-65 heavy chain [Mus musculus]               367     3e-126  85%       \r\n2A6D_B Chain B, Germline antibody 36-65 Fab Heavy chain [Mus m...  363     1e-124  84%       \r\nWIW78152.1 anti-panfilovirus glycoprotein specific immunoglobu...  369     1e-123  88%       \r\n1YUH_B Chain B, 88C6/12 FAB (HEAVY CHAIN) [Mus musculus]           360     2e-123  80%       \r\nAAS77396.1 anti-GD3 monoclonal antibody 3D2 immunoglobulin hea...  368     2e-123  86%       \r\n9S8W_H Chain H, A54 Fab heavy chain [Mus musculus]                 360     2e-123  84%       \r\n"]
